Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.37,0:00:11.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.73,0:00:14.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没能做早饭的说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.37,0:00:15.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么傻话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.68,0:00:16.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都发高烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.09,0:00:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我躺着 我帮你给学校打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.00,0:00:22.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚饭你也不用做 好好睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.47,0:00:24.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得令
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.44,0:00:25.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,及川
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.49,0:00:26.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.33,0:00:27.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙坂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.05,0:00:30.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…哦 乙坂感冒 请了病假
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.09,0:00:31.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加藤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.95,0:00:32.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.78,0:00:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木岛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.70,0:00:34.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.64,0:00:35.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木山
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.56,0:00:36.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.52,0:00:37.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.63,0:00:38.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.56,0:00:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小松
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.55,0:00:40.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.57,0:00:41.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小宫山
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.43,0:00:41.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到…
