Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.87,0:02:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能力是 崩毁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.30,0:02:47.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,崩毁？什么能力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.09,0:02:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.13,0:02:51.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能将盯上的东西毁坏之类的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:55.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…不过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.69,0:02:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不叫破坏 这名字有点可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.30,0:02:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,位置呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.38,0:03:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.60,0:03:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 这是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.26,0:03:04.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们学校的配套公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:07.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 有能力者也正常吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.87,0:03:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:09.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.51,0:03:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标现在就在公寓里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.18,0:03:13.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不觉得奇怪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.01,0:03:14.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.25,0:03:17.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父母是不会变成能力者的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.99,0:03:20.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为能力仅出现于青春期
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.61,0:03:21.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.77,0:03:23.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.57,0:03:26.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是感冒了没来上学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.57,0:03:28.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.61,0:03:32.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 你这慌张的样子可不一般
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:34.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是凑巧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:36.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么凑巧？说来听听
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.77,0:03:40.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妹妹…发烧卧床
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.93,0:03:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…兄妹都有能力的概率果然很大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.03,0:03:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦 我们又不是科学家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.55,0:03:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先去给步未妹妹探探病
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.77,0:03:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便探探她有没有获得能力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.69,0:04:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 你们要一起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.88,0:04:03.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她生着病呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.32,0:04:04.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.20,0:04:07.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就我一个人去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.27,0:04:09.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢着 步未是柚咲的歌迷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.33,0:04:13.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果带柚咲过去 步未一定会很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.92,0:04:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 追星的你很碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.76,0:04:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要友利和柚咲去就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.22,0:04:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入侵后跳楼 让你受点伤好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.10,0:04:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 原来长颈鹿是那样睡觉的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:31.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀 长颈鹿会在睡觉时把脖子卷起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.86,0:04:33.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…呃 什么 有长颈鹿吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.84,0:04:35.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪？在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:44.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼 我觉得他不适合同去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.40,0:04:45.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友利 干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.56,0:04:47.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.33,0:04:49.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他全身都穿了防具
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:52.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是头着地就没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.06,0:04:56.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人受伤 请马上派救护车过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:05:00.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我们三个放学后去探病吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.83,0:05:05.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先让我去便利店买点慰问品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.37,0:05:09.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好呀 我也想买点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.07,0:05:13.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也正好想买点速食粥再回去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.92,0:05:17.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我们晚上也和步未一起吃粥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.23,0:05:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.90,0:05:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们回家后爱吃什么吃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.24,0:05:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不方便的话 我们就回家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.16,0:05:27.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起吃才好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.83,0:05:28.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.77,0:05:29.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.75,0:05:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我远离父母 回到家也只会孤单
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.04,0:05:38.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是习惯了孤单
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:40.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑羽同学刚搬来不久
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能还不习惯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.69,0:05:45.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不止是柚咲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.13,0:05:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在心里发誓 不再相信任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.98,0:05:52.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并逃出了那所「学校」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.89,0:05:55.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被母亲卖给科学家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.19,0:05:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得不相信任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:05:59.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在也是孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.01,0:06:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有妹妹的我 是多么的幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.51,0:06:06.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 晚上大家一起吃粥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.92,0:06:09.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1360日元
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:11.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超出预算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.81,0:06:13.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我来付
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.05,0:06:14.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加上这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.22,0:06:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要…滑子菇？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.16,0:06:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？滑子菇强爆了好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:23.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加在粥里吃也很搭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:26.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你自己喜欢吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.25,0:06:29.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行吧 反正是你付钱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 让我来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劳驾 我想要那盒曲奇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.52,0:06:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？第一次见到有人买那个！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.06,0:06:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2500日元
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.78,0:06:40.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且好贵！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.01,0:06:43.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有专门的纸袋子装？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.45,0:06:44.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次见到人买的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.89,0:06:47.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次见到这纸袋子！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.82,0:06:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.85,0:06:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.21,0:07:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妹妹是你的狂热歌迷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.61,0:07:03.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更加期待和她见面了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.70,0:07:06.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 她现在正发烧卧病在床
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.91,0:07:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让她太兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:10.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她肯定会流鼻血
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.71,0:07:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.87,0:07:13.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 不能突然见面 要慢慢来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:17.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要「咦？莫非是柚咲琳？」这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.36,0:07:21.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 我先戴个口罩来变装
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.88,0:07:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.78,0:07:27.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 你们先在这等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.63,0:07:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？有客人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.82,0:07:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.28,0:07:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有宇哥哥回来了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:43.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:45.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥大人你好 打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:47.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是班长 野村
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.16,0:07:50.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是来探望小步未的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.82,0:07:53.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫及川
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:58.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和令妹相处愉快 还请您多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.82,0:08:01.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 看你这献媚的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.11,0:08:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都被甩过一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想让小步未更加讨厌你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.72,0:08:06.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.70,0:08:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是向步未表白后被甩的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.35,0:08:10.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.27,0:08:15.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么多人上门叨扰 真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.96,0:08:18.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.34,0:08:20.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥大人 给你添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小步未 多保重哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.13,0:08:34.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.34,0:08:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.54,0:08:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该说正在打扰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:38.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 我还没叫你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？我还以为是换班制呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.84,0:08:44.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 是友利姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.43,0:08:46.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 我们又见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.40,0:08:50.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 莫非现在是哥哥的女朋友了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.41,0:08:51.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.37,0:08:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？明明很配…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.45,0:08:56.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 还有一位客人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:58.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:02.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 柚 咲 琳 ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一下子就暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.44,0:09:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来止血
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.09,0:09:10.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用嘴呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 止住了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.51,0:09:20.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦 止住了 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:23.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.06,0:09:26.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 柚 咲 琳 ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.34,0:09:28.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来止血
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要用止鼻血的魔法？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.99,0:09:33.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别 会适得其反的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.57,0:09:38.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲眼见柚咲琳 大吃一惊的说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:40.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于冷静了么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.58,0:09:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哇哇 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这是慰问品 曲奇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.44,0:09:46.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把它放这喽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.74,0:09:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪…哪里哪里 让柚咲琳大人费心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.34,0:09:52.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 她只是我的同班同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.25,0:09:54.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别太着迷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.51,0:09:55.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.97,0:09:57.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哇哇…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.71,0:09:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还被传染了口头禅！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:03.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的慰问品呢 是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.50,0:10:06.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦 我很喜欢！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.18,0:10:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有食欲吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.68,0:10:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我买了速食粥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥吃什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:12.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也吃粥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.23,0:10:14.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦！大家一起吃粥！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:17.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开吃喽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:22.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超级超级好吃的说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.44,0:10:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:26.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.68,0:10:28.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.80,0:10:33.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.07,0:10:35.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:36.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.84,0:10:39.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.35,0:10:40.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.61,0:10:44.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我要去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.32,0:10:45.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.76,0:10:47.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是活动频繁的艺人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.15,0:10:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许有意见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:52.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦 正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.41,0:10:54.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请努力投身工作之中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.73,0:10:55.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我就此作别
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:58.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步未妹妹 多保重哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:11:02.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚咲琳大人 谢谢你来看我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.65,0:11:05.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢感激感动得不得了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.48,0:11:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 来收拾东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:12.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？放着不洗吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.24,0:11:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点东西 随时都能洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.02,0:11:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你小子啥血型？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.96,0:11:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在立刻洗掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.94,0:11:22.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洗好后你负责用布擦 懂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.46,0:11:23.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.06,0:11:35.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 你们俩果然是在瞒着我谈恋爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.62,0:11:36.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.79,0:11:40.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好同步呀 是在掩饰害羞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.10,0:11:41.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.23,0:11:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.54,0:11:45.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得你们真的很配哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里哪里 这家伙又帅又聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.26,0:11:51.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我根本配不上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.79,0:11:52.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈 哈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:54.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.42,0:11:56.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得有宇哥哥能和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.54,0:11:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他的福气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.39,0:11:59.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别被骗啊 步未
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.12,0:12:02.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她叫我「这家伙」啊 不觉得很矛盾吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.69,0:12:06.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了 闭上嘴巴看电视去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:13.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好快！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.30,0:12:15.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚咲琳的移动速度好快！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.94,0:12:17.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是录播
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.40,0:12:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对哦
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//----------------------------TXTB----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.47,0:12:27.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喏 吃药
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.55,0:12:33.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天要早睡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:35.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来给你盖被子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.15,0:12:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有个好哥哥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.62,0:12:43.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.84,0:12:46.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…但是 我有点怕睡着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.93,0:12:48.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.86,0:12:51.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白天 我做了个噩梦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.38,0:12:56.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发烧的人 的确容易做噩梦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.42,0:12:58.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:00.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 你梦见什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.61,0:13:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让她回想噩梦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:05.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.11,0:13:07.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.25,0:13:09.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.61,0:13:12.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待您再次光临本店
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.27,0:13:12.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.40,0:13:14.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去送送她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:15.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.02,0:13:17.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咻咻咻～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.91,0:13:19.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了 没交往
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.58,0:13:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问出噩梦的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这或许会成为「崩毁」能力的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.42,0:13:29.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.34,0:13:32.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有证据证明步未是特殊能力者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.85,0:13:35.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也可能是这栋楼里的其他人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.77,0:13:37.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确没有证据
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:40.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 可能性非常高
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 「崩毁」…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.08,0:13:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有种危险的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:49.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我最初感受到的那种恐怖么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.00,0:13:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 请你问出究竟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:53.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是为了步未妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.19,0:13:56.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.83,0:14:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使烧退了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天也要让她休息 以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.12,0:14:07.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 我们手上的情报太少了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:09.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.65,0:14:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:20.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 步未
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:24.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我说说那个梦的内容好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.73,0:14:28.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…我也记不清了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.46,0:14:29.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说个大概就行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.87,0:14:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:32.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个坏掉的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:34.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么坏掉？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.57,0:14:36.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…是地面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.15,0:14:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么样的地面？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…想不起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.25,0:14:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地面出现裂缝 然后分开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.39,0:14:48.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要问这种问题呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.39,0:14:52.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是预言梦 不就糟了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.50,0:14:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种超自然的东西 我可不信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:15:00.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这世上到处都是超自然的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.15,0:15:03.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地面分开？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.57,0:15:06.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在暗示什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.65,0:15:08.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个能力说不定很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.58,0:15:11.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会把能力者本人也卷进去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.53,0:15:16.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…情报实在是太少了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.34,0:15:17.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.42,0:15:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我们能做的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.20,0:15:23.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是借助初中部的大量摄像头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.72,0:15:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用它们来观察能力的倾向
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后就是 让教师去提醒步未妹妹注意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.60,0:15:35.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初中部的人很多 一旦出事就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:37.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是公寓比较安全
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.50,0:15:39.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还想再收集些情报
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.68,0:15:41.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请让她明天继续休息
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:43.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.61,0:15:46.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要我去施展治感冒的魔法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.11,0:15:50.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出现了！柚咲琳的小魔法之21
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:54.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,治愈感冒的魔法！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.06,0:15:55.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好恶心！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.28,0:15:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用 她又会流鼻血的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.42,0:15:58.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就别去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:15:59.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:01.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就等她康复后再说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.41,0:16:03.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.39,0:16:08.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,36.5度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.56,0:16:10.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烧退了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.42,0:16:16.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功击退病魔的我会一如既往 继续努力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:18.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没做怪梦吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.80,0:16:19.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.26,0:16:24.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你的病刚好 再休息一天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:25.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.89,0:16:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没发烧却躺床上会很无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.49,0:16:30.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想上学的说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.63,0:16:32.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感冒有可能再犯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.91,0:16:34.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做哥哥的不能让你去上学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:37.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍一忍 乖乖地再睡一天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.57,0:16:38.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:40.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去跟学校说一声
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.86,0:16:42.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶～！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.80,0:16:56.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以步未之能 岂能再遭拦截
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.49,0:17:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,披萨酱的仇 我来报
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.69,0:17:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的伤好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:14.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.21,0:17:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说我前天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.56,0:17:18.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从学生会室被踢下去的事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.38,0:17:20.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.15,0:17:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经常会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:24.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种小变故 我应对起来也很快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.96,0:17:26.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 刚认识她时
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.64,0:17:28.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很快就进了医院
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.74,0:17:32.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我是你 绝对要跑路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.71,0:17:35.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友利真的适合领军吗 我有点不安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:39.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她比你想的更精于算计
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.35,0:17:46.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 又在叫我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.76,0:17:47.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.52,0:17:52.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.41,0:17:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们吃的都是意大利面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.00,0:17:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没法全扒进嘴里 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:17:59.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然有闲心用叉子卷面条！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.08,0:18:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么 出什么事了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.76,0:18:04.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步未妹妹来上学了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:05.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.60,0:18:09.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 我和学校说过了 她今天请病假
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.44,0:18:10.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她早上的状态如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.10,0:18:12.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烧退了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.81,0:18:14.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我告诉她 感冒有可能再犯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.45,0:18:16.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让她再休息一天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.89,0:18:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为退烧了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.13,0:18:22.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她似乎自作主张 第三节课就来上学了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.72,0:18:23.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.61,0:18:25.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有种不祥的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.84,0:18:27.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻去看看步未妹妹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.54,0:18:39.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:43.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 乙坂同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.03,0:18:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到了一家年糕红豆汤很棒的甜品店
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.00,0:18:49.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为康复的贺礼 我请你吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.25,0:18:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.26,0:18:53.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我病刚好 就不去吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.59,0:18:56.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等 等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.14,0:19:00.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,病刚好不能吃 那就周末…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.71,0:19:01.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咚！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.89,0:19:05.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你小子真不识相
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.79,0:19:07.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都被甩过一次了还不放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.03,0:19:10.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让开 我要努力挽回啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.61,0:19:12.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啰嗦啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.19,0:19:13.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙由我来对付
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.30,0:19:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先走吧 小步未
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.85,0:19:18.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 谢谢你 小野
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.38,0:19:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.46,0:19:20.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙…乙坂同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.72,0:19:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说 你死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.31,0:19:24.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 你去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.11,0:19:26.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抄近路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.24,0:19:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.19,0:19:33.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小西同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.22,0:19:36.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪你转进来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.09,0:19:39.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.33,0:19:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和及川同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.91,0:19:42.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和及川同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.87,0:19:46.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和及川同学一起吃便当
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.17,0:19:48.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成双成对的是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.71,0:19:52.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你转进来之后…及川同学他！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.35,0:19:57.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,及川同学他就像忘了我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:19:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼里变得只有你！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.50,0:20:10.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 我们好好谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.62,0:20:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一定是误会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.21,0:20:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 快把刀收起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.84,0:20:16.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.93,0:20:19.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.81,0:20:22.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.17,0:20:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.41,0:20:54.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.37,0:20:55.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.62,0:20:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才会遭殃！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.73,0:20:59.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.27,0:21:02.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁来…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.31,0:21:04.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁来！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.48,0:21:09.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.04,0:21:32.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是…崩毁…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.08,0:21:37.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没赶上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.52,0:21:43.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.15,0:21:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.76,0:21:45.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步未
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.09,0:21:47.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步未！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.59,0:21:49.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别去 会被波及的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.51,0:21:54.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步未！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.18,0:22:05.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同学！快离开那里 很危险！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.44,0:22:06.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步未
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.82,0:22:07.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步未
